subSubSection.paragraph:
Female (
allotype
): similar to male in general body shape. Gonads paired, opposed; ovaries outstretched, not reflexed. Anterior and posterior ovaries located on the left and right side of intestine, respectively. Vulval opening ventral, located in the middle of the body. Vagina short, not thickened. Two glands surrounding the vulva. Tail 150 µm long (c' =7.5).
